<p style="text-align: right;">=] אקולוקו שולט</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/trolaemarII1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1192" title="trolaemarII" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/trolaemarII1.jpg" alt="" width="249" height="204" /></a></p>
